image_analysis.description: A photograph of a page from a book or report. The left side of the page contains printed text. The right side of the page features four photographs with corresponding captions. The photographs include an aerial view of a waterfront property, a group of three young women, a black and white yearbook photo of a young man, and a color photo of a young man on a beach. A page number is visible at the bottom left, and a document identifier is at the bottom right.
image_analysis.layout: Two-column layout. The left column is a block of text. The right column is a collection of images with captions.
